item.title: CVE-2023-49108|2024-08-02T21:46:29.150Z -- sumitomo%20electric%20information%20systems%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- rakrak%20document%20plus
item.description: Path traversal vulnerability exists in RakRak Document Plus Ver.3.2.0.0 to Ver.6.4.0.7 (excluding Ver.6.1.1.3a). If this vulnerability is exploited, arbitrary files on the server may be obtained or deleted by a user of the product with specific privileges.
